emptydir - to store data at pod level
hostPath: this volume mounts a file from host node file system into our pod, all pods on same node can use data
Persistent volume (external storage) - available across cluster
Persistent volume claim: finds appropriate volume and binds it
storage classes  - how the pv should be created, not created in any namespace -- availabe to entire cluster

** pvc dependent on pod
   pvd depend on pvc
pods created by developers, pv created by admin

